 finance advisory firm formerly known as lexicon partners since  and chairman of the management board and investment committee at living bridge equity partners llp a private equity firm formerly known as isis equity partners llp since  both based in the united kingdom  she has been a member of the supervisory board and chairman of the audit committee of basf a leading chemical company based in germany since  and she has served as a director of zurich insurance group since   she previously served as nonexecutive chairman of mf global holdings ltd  and as a director of the man group plc  malachite a uk consulting firm  barclays plc  and friends provident plc  all united kingdom based companies  she has served as a director of the company since   beth e ford beth e ford age  is executive vice president chief supply chain and operations officer at land o’lakes a memberowned agricultural production and dairy cooperative and has held that position since   ms ford served as executive vice president and head of supply chain at international flavor and fragrances   ms ford has served as a director of clearwater paper corporation since   she is on the dean’s advisory committee for the college of business at iowa state university and the board of advisors at the columbia university business school  she has served as a director of the company since  kirk s hachigian kirk s hachigian age  is chairman president and chief executive officer of jeldwen inc a global manufacturer of windows and doors and has held that position since april   he previously served as a principal of skykarr capital llc a private investment firm from  to march  and as chairman president and chief executive officer of cooper industries plc a  billion global manufacturer of electrical products from  until it was acquired by eaton corporation in   he has served as lead director for allegion plc and as a director of nextera energy inc since   he has served as a director of the company since  luiz kaufmann luiz kaufmann age  is managing partner of l kaufmann consultants in sao paulo brasil a company which provides investment banking services and operational leadership in mergers and acquisitions and has held that position since   he currently also serves as ceo and is a director of el tejar limited a bermudabased company that has agriculture and livestock operations in south america and has held that position since   he also serves on the advisory council for nubank e and endless mobile since   he previously served as president and ceo of kroton educacional  and as president and ceo  and as a director  of medial saude  he previously served as a director of several brazilian companies including gol a brazilian airline  and vivo the largest mobile telecom company in brasil   he previously held ceo positions at several brazilian companies including aracruz celulose the largest eucalyptus pulp producer in the world  and grupo multiplic  a diversified financial group  he also served as the managing director of arthur d little in brasil   he has served as a director of the company since  roderick c mcgeary roderick c mcgeary age  served in consulting and audit roles with kpmg llp from  to  culminating in the position as covice chairman of consulting  he was chairman of bearingpoint inc formerly kpmg consulting llc a management and technology consulting firm from  to  and was its interim chief executive officer from  to  bearingpoint filed for protection under chapter  of the us bankruptcy code in february  and its plan under chapter  was declared effective as of december   he has served as a director of cisco systems since  he previously served as nonexecutive chairman of tegile systems inc  and as a director of dionex corporation  and national semiconductor corporation  he has served as a director of the company since  john m pigott john m pigott age  is a partner in beta business ventures llc a private investment company concentrating in natural resources and was a partner in the predecessor company beta capital group llc since   he is the brother of mark c pigott a director of the company  he has served as a director of the company since  mark c pigott mark c pigott age  is executive chairman of the company and has held that position since april   mr pigott was chairman and chief executive officer of the company from january  to april  vice chairman from january  to december  executive vice president from december  to january  senior vice president from january  to december  and vice president from october  to december   he has served as a director of franklin resources inc an investment management company since   he is the brother of john m pigott a director of the company  he has served as a director of the company since   mark a schulz mark a schulz age  served as president of international operations at ford motor company from  until his retirement in   he is currently president and chief executive officer of m a schulz and associates a management consulting firm and a founding partner in fontinalis partners llc a transportation technology strategic investment firm  he has served as a director of dana holdings corporation since  and previously served as a director of yrc worldwide inc  and as a director of the national committee of united stateschina relations and the united stateschina business council  he has served as a director of the company since  gregory m e spierkel gregory m e spierkel age  served as chief executive officer of ingram micro inc a  billion worldwide distributor of technology products from  to   he previously served as president from march  to april   during his year tenure with that company he held other senior positions including executive vice president  he was also a director of ingram micro   he has served as a director of mgm resorts international since  and as a director of schneider electric paris since october   he has served as a director of the company since   charles r williamson charles r williamson age  has served as chairman of the board of weyerhaeuser company a forest products company since  and served as chairman of talisman energy inc a canadian oil and gas company  he served as chairman and chief executive officer of unocal the californiabased energy company from  until unocal merged with chevron in august  mr williamson was the chairman of the usasean business council  he has served as a director of the company since  and serves as lead director back to top a world of opportunity awaits learn about careers at paccar ➝   paccar inc all rights reserved privacy statement terms of use site map for technical problems involving this site contact internet producer mark pigott  wikipedia mark pigott from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search a major contributor to this article appears to have a close connection with its subject it may require cleanup to comply with wikipedias content policies particularly neutral point of view please discuss further on the talk page october  learn how and when to remove this template message mark pigott mark pigott kbe born february   is an american businessman he is executive chairman of the board of directors of paccar since april  he was chairman and chief executive officer of paccar inc from january  to april  pigott has been highlighted as one of the nations leading ceos by forbes magazine in their annual listing of the top ten ceos in the country contents  education  business career  philanthropy  awards and honors  references  other sources  external links educationedit mark pigott was born in san francisco and raised in seattle he has lived in many cities in north america studied in italy and worked in the united kingdom from  to  he graduated from stanford university receiving his bs in industrial engineering  an ms in business  and a ba in humanities  he has received an honorary doctorate in science sc d from trinity college dublin  an honorary doctorate of laws lld from gonzaga university  an honorary doctorate of humane letters dhl from lehman college ny  and a dhl from seattle university wa  an honorary doctorate of fine arts from the university of puget sound wa  and an honorary doctorate of humane letters from the university of washington wa  business careeredit mark pigotts successful career with paccar began in  he is the fourth generation of the pigott family to lead the company paccar a fortune  company celebrated its th year in  and has earned  years of consecutive profitability paccar revenues  billion nasdaqpcar is publicly traded and is a global technology leader in the capital goods and financial services industries paccars major brands are daf trucks kenworth and peterbilt trucks paccar financial paclease paccar parts and paccar information technology under mark pigotts leadership as chairman and ceo paccar has delivered a  percent total return to shareholders pigotts focus on quality and innovation has resulted in paccar receiving many jd power and associates awards for highest customer satisfaction as well as international truck of the year awards paccar has earned the distinction of being one of the nations leading companies by forbes barrons businessweek industryweek and informationweek magazine pigott has been chairman of the daf supervisory board since  served on the business council washington dc retired and on the washington state business roundtable executive committee retired harvard business review january  named pigott as one of the top  global ceos based on long term shareholder returns philanthropyedit mark pigott is president of the paccar foundation which annually donates – million in support of education social services and the arts beneficiaries included university of north texas  stanford university  mississippi state university  gonzaga university  east mississippi community college  university of washington  seattle university  university of puget sound  and washington state university  pigott established the prestigious paccar award for teaching excellence at the university of washington in  this is the highest honorarium teaching award for mba professors in the united states pigotts strong support of corporate giving is demonstrated by the fact that in  paccar was ranked fifth on a list of  top large corporate philanthropists in the state of washington by the puget sound business journal book of lists on a personal basis pigott has funded professorships and scholarships at stanford university trinity college dublin the university of washington gonzaga university kings college cambridge cambridge university and trinity college dublin he purchased a seat on the board of the royal shakespeare company america the british library foundation st georges society new york advisory board and trinity college foundation he is a life member of the national gallery london the british library royal society for the encouragement of arts manufacture commerce rsa and the royal national theatre uk major philanthropy also includes strategic planning and implementation of capital projects at st pauls cathedral london the royal shakespeare company national gallery uk and trinity college dublin an avid bibliophile mark pigott is involved in numerous projects benefiting the british library and the folger shakespeare library for over a decade his dedication to educating the next generation of leaders is evidenced by his participation as a lecturer at numerous graduate schools of business including the university of washington seattle university gonzaga university stanford and trinity college dublin awards and honorsedit mark pigott has been awarded numerous honors awards and knighthoods over the course of his career notable awards include year award or honor organization country  knight of the order of st john  venerable order of saint john united states  chevalier of orders and letters french culture france  inducted into industry weeks manufacturing hall of fame industry week united states  honorary knight commander of the most excellent order of the british empire kbe order of the british empire united kingdom  medal of honor from the st georges society of new york st georges society of new york united states  cross of the order of merit republic of hungary hungary  commander of the order of st john venerable order of saint john united states  guild of benefactors cambridge university united kingdom  officer of the order of orangenassau order of orangenassau netherlands  stanford university governors’ award for over  years of dedicated service to the university stanford university united states  albert schweitzer leadership award hoby hugh obrian youth hoby organization united states  ellis island medal of honor  national ethnic coalition of organizations neco united states  commander of the order of the crown belgium kingdom of belgium belgium  honoree of the ireland chamber of commerce iccusa ireland chamber of commerce ireland  irish america magazine business  list irish america magazine ireland  washington state ceo of the year washington ceo magazine united states  officer of the order of the british empire obe order of the british empire united kingdom referencesedit  mark pigott executive profile  biography  businessweek investingbusinessweekcom retrieved  june    forbes – ceo compensation performance v pay rank  forbes   stanford school of engineering alumni profile soeoldwebserverstanfordedu retrieved  october    trinity college dublin annual report  pdf tcdie retrieved  october    lehman today fall   winter  pdf lehmanedu retrieved  october     archived february   at the wayback machine  httpswwwwashingtoneduregentsfilesbpdf  pcar stock quote  paccar inc stock price  nasdaqcom nasdaqcom retrieved  october    about us  paccar paccarcom retrieved  october    open line  may   edition · university of puget sound pugetsoundedu retrieved  october    wsu honors major donation from paccar wsu news retrieved  october    jain wins  paccar award for excellence i