earn how and when to remove this template message mark pigott mark pigott kbe born february   is an american businessman he is executive chairman of the board of directors of paccar since april  he was chairman and chief executive officer of paccar inc from january  to april  pigott has been highlighted as one of the nations leading ceos by forbes magazine in their annual listing of the top ten ceos in the country contents  education  business career  philanthropy  awards and honors  references  other sources  external links educationedit mark pigott was born in san francisco and raised in seattle he has lived in many cities in north america studied in italy and worked in the united kingdom from  to  he graduated from stanford university receiving his bs in industrial engineering  an ms in business  and a ba in humanities  he has received an honorary doctorate in science sc d from trinity college dublin  an honorary doctorate of laws lld from gonzaga university  an honorary doctorate of humane letters dhl from lehman college ny  and a dhl from seattle university wa  an honorary doctorate of fine arts from the university of puget sound wa  and an honorary doctorate of humane letters from the university of washington wa  business careeredit mark pigotts successful career with paccar began in  he is the fourth generation of the pigott family to lead the company paccar a fortune  company celebrated its th year in  and has earned  years of consecutive profitability paccar revenues  billion nasdaqpcar is publicly traded and is a global technology leader in the capital goods and financial services industries paccars major brands are daf trucks kenworth and peterbilt trucks paccar financial paclease paccar parts and paccar information technology under mark pigotts leadership as chairman and ceo paccar has delivered a  percent total return to shareholders pigotts focus on quality and innovation has resulted in paccar receiving many jd power and associates awards for highest customer satisfaction as well as international truck of the year awards paccar has earned the distinction of being one of the nations leading companies by forbes barrons businessweek industryweek and informationweek magazine pigott has been chairman of the daf supervisory board since  served on the business council washington dc retired and on the washington state business roundtable executive committee retired harvard business review january  named pigott as one of the top  global ceos based on long term shareholder returns philanthropyedit mark pigott is president of the paccar foundation which annually donates – million in support of education social services and the arts beneficiaries included university of north texas  stanford university  mississippi state university  gonzaga university  east mississippi community college  university of washington  seattle university  university of puget sound  and washington state university  pigott established the prestigious paccar award for teaching excellence at the university of washington in  this is the highest honorarium teaching award for mba professors in the united states pigotts strong support of corporate giving is demonstrated by the fact that in  paccar was ranked fifth on a list of  top large corporate philanthropists in the state of washington by the puget sound business journal book of lists on a personal basis pigott has funded professorships and scholarships at stanford university trinity college dublin the university of washington gonzaga university kings college cambridge cambridge university and trinity college dublin he purchased a seat on the board of the royal shakespeare company america the british library foundation st georges society new york advisory board and trinity college foundation he is a life member of the national gallery london the british library royal society for the encouragement of arts manufacture commerce rsa and the royal national theatre uk major philanthropy also includes strategic planning and implementation of capital projects at st pauls cathedral london the royal shakespeare company national gallery uk and trinity college dublin an avid bibliophile mark pigott is involved in numerous projects benefiting the british library and the folger shakespeare library for over a decade his dedication to educating the next generation of leaders is evidenced by his participation as a lecturer at numerous graduate schools of business including the university of washington seattle university gonzaga university stanford and trinity college dublin awards and honorsedit mark pigott has been awarded numerous honors awards and knighthoods over the course of his career notable awards include year award or honor organization country  knight of the order of st john  venerable order of saint john united states  chevalier of orders and letters french culture france  inducted into industry weeks manufacturing hall of fame industry week united states  honorary knight commander of the most excellent order of the british empire kbe order of the british empire united kingdom  medal of honor from the st georges society of new york st georges society of new york united states  cross of the order of merit republic of hungary hungary  commander of the order of st john venerable order of saint john united states  guild of benefactors cambridge university united kingdom  officer of the order of orangenassau order of orangenassau netherlands  stanford university governors’ award for over  years of dedicated service to the university stanford university united states  albert schweitzer leadership award hoby hugh obrian youth hoby organization united states  ellis island medal of honor  national ethnic coalition of organizations neco united states  commander of the order of the crown belgium kingdom of belgium belgium  honoree of the ireland chamber of commerce iccusa ireland chamber of commerce ireland  irish america magazine business  list irish america magazine ireland  washington state ceo of the year washington ceo magazine united states  officer of the order of the british empire obe order of the british empire united kingdom referencesedit  mark pigott executive profile  biography  businessweek investingbusinessweekcom retrieved  june    forbes – ceo compensation performance v pay rank  forbes   stanford school of engineering alumni profile soeoldwebserverstanfordedu retrieved  october    trinity college dublin annual report  pdf tcdie retrieved  october    lehman today fall   winter  pdf lehmanedu retrieved  october     archived february   at the wayback machine  httpswwwwashingtoneduregentsfilesbpdf  pcar stock quote  paccar inc stock price  nasdaqcom nasdaqcom retrieved  october    about us  paccar paccarcom retrieved  october    open line  may   edition · university of puget sound pugetsoundedu retrieved  october    wsu honors major donation from paccar wsu news retrieved  october    jain wins  paccar award for excellence in teaching fosterwashingtonedu retrieved  october    top corporate philanthropists companies with more than m revenue puget sound business journal  may  retrieved  october    book of lists  puget sound business journal puget sound business journal retrieved  october    why mark pigott supports cambridge archived  at the wayback machine cambridge university development office  american history lectureship established at trinity college archived  at the wayback machine dublin may    rsc america rscorguk retrieved  october    the british library  the worlds knowledge bluk retrieved  october     archived july   at the wayback machine  development trinity college dublin  march  development tcdie retrieved  october    the national gallery london nationalgalleryorguk retrieved  october    rsa  home rsaorguk retrieved  october    members online booking national theatre archived from the original on  july  retrieved  october    a b american millionaire mark pigott lavishes gifts on uk mucketycom december    a b ht